  "notes": "Champions: Monsters.\n\nCombos:\n-Apple of His Eye (choose monsters) + Edormira = only event immune or champion power immune champions can defend.\n-Attacking with Harkon Lucas, pick the one psionicist, hero or cleric in the pool, win, then attack with a different champion with the sword and helm to raze.\n\nPlaying tips:\nIf Belly of the Beast Dungeon leaves play, Winneer's Trophy will help with unarmed combat cards.  Also T'chaar and Gellidus (with Good Defense) can use them.\n\nRuling links:\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind0006D&L=spellfire-l&P=R529\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind9903D&L=spellfire-l&D=0&P=4455",
